						select#PS(onchange="window.location.href= '/casa-e-jardim/black---decker?' + 'PS=' + this.options[this.selectedIndex].value")
						option(selected='selected', value='12') 12
						option(value='24') 24
						option(value='36') 36
						option(value='48') 48
					p.compare
						| Produtos selecionados para comparar:
						strong
						span#NumeroSuperior.compare-selection-count 0
						a.btn-comparar(title='Comparar', href='#') Comparar
				.vitrine.resultItemsWrapper

					#PagerTop_52435197.pager.top
